<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103792>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–5. Male aedeagi of North American Lechriops. 1) Lechriops californicus (LeConte) (specimen from AZ: E. Turkey Creek, 6.5 mi W Portal, 29.05.1997, H.A. Hespenheide (CHAH)); 2) L. variegatus n. sp. (specimen from AZ: Chiricahua Mts., Rustler Pk., 29.06.1958, C. W. O’Brien (CWOB)); 3) L. oblongulus Champion (specimen from AZ: Chiricahua Mts., 8,0009, 30.07.1957, C. W. O’Brien (CHAH)); 4) L. chiricahuae n. sp. (specimen from AZ: Flagstaff, 30.07.1938, D.J. and J.N. Knull (CHAH)); 5) L. oculatus (Say) (specimen from CT: Storrs, 24.06.1973, H.A. Hespenheide (CHAH))." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

